oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Pocket testament and inscription of Pvt. Henry E. Phillips
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This pocket edition of the New Testament has contact information written in indelible pencil on the inside cover and has two other inscriptions in pencil with one dated 2/5/28. Phillips was from Oliver Springs, Tennessee. The town limits includes portions of Morgan, Roane, and Anderson Counties.
